    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Names may not be everything, but CHRIS EVERT seemed suitably impressed yesterday at the formal unveiling of the official trophy for the Matrix Essentials Evert Cup, which will be held in Indian Wells, Calif., from Feb. 22-28. She was also, perhaps, a bit puzzled. The Evert Cup, it turns out, is no cup at all, but a truncated chunk of Baccarat crystal that wouldn't hold so much as a sip of champagne.</p>
      </block>
